"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-olympic-eventing-equestrian-team-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Equestrian Boyd Martin is going to his fourth Olympics as part of the three-rider U.S. eventing team for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"score\": 0.7689707838437181, \"rank\": 0.30043291783643256, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Martin, 44, is joined on the roster by Will Coleman, a 41-year-old going to his second Olympics after a 2012 London Games appearance, and Caroline Pamukcu, a 29-year-old going to her first Games.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"score\": 0.7689707838437181, \"rank\": 0.30043291783643256, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 162, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Will_Coleman_(American_football)\", \"score\": 0.9999971214017982, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Will Coleman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Will_Coleman_(American_football)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Will_Coleman_(American_football)\"}, {\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Records\", \"score\": 0.5726966393591035, \"rank\": 0.449632707967465, \"text\": \"Caroline\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q18127\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Records\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Records\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Martin, whose best individual Olympic finish is 16th, is now ranked third in the world.\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"score\": 0.7689707838437181, \"rank\": 0.30043291783643256, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A dual citizen, he was in the running to make Olympic teams in 2000, 2004 and 2008 for his native Australia before he began riding for the U.S. in 2009 after moving in 2007.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.5656072143890348, \"rank\": 0.5476767003471692, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LIST:U.S. athletes qualified for Paris Olympics  Phillip Dutton, who was in the running to make an eighth Olympic team at age 60, was not named to the team.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Dutton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phillip Dutton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Dutton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Dutton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was bidding to become the oldest U.S. Olympian since art competitions were held at the Games in the 1930s, according to the OlyMADMen.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9938686277839449, \"rank\": 0.006169197864506608, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dutton is ranked 44th in the world and sixth among Americans.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 881, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/E._P._Dutton\", \"score\": 0.9961626360804566, \"rank\": 0.003836303187298602, \"text\": \"Dutton\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/E._P._Dutton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/E._P._Dutton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was ranked 10th in the world last September.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His horse at the Tokyo Games - Z - is rehabbing from injury, and his other international horses are less experienced at the highest levels.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Phillip Dutton has been a mainstay within the U.S. program and contributed to many of the successes of the U.S. Eventing Team over the past two decades,\\\" U.S. Equestrian Director of FEI Sport Hallye Griffin said in an email.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Dutton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phillip Dutton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Dutton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phillip_Dutton\"}, {\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 125